WEBVTT

00:00:01.440 --> 00:00:03.830
Oh wow, there's already that.

00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:05.910
Well, good evening family. Thank you

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:07.670
for joining us.

00:00:07.680 --> 00:00:10.310
That number shot up fast, so you

00:00:10.310 --> 00:00:10.320
all

00:00:10.320 --> 00:00:12.310
had your notifications on. Thank

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:13.310
you.

