00:00:27.080 --> 00:00:28.630
heart right now.

00:00:28.640 --> 00:00:32.269
Braden made that short

00:00:32.279 --> 00:00:34.750
little clip

00:00:34.750 --> 00:00:34.760
of

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:36.350
