00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:43.150
I didn't realize that

00:00:43.160 --> 00:00:45.710
the Lord had spoken to us over 80 times

00:00:45.720 --> 00:00:47.710
to watch

00:00:47.710 --> 00:00:47.720
Cuba—over

00:00:47.720 --> 00:00:49.510
80 times. Braden didn't put them

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:50.990
all on there

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:52.310
