00:01:00.760 --> 00:01:02.310
to see if we're missing

00:01:02.320 --> 00:01:03.430
anything

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:05.150
and what we've brought out

00:01:05.160 --> 00:01:07.550
to the people, because it's

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:09.790
all buried. There are so many videos;

00:01:09.800 --> 00:01:11.710
everything's buried. So I said, 'Go

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:14.150
through it,'and it took him days to do

00:01:14.160 --> 00:01:15.590
that. Last night he was tired, and I

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:17.310
told him, 'Well, you worked so

00:01:17.320 --> 00:01:19.150
hard doing that, we won't do a live

00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:20.270
stream.

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:23.590
I'll upload that video and

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:26.830
they can have that for today.'So, that

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:28.190
was interesting.

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:30.030
Braden said

00:01:33.360 --> 00:01:35.270
it

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:37.670
was 80 different

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:40.310
videos of different times the Lord

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:42.830
had spoken about it. I thought it

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:44.630
was pretty interesting. It's a

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:46.910
hot topic, in other words.

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:48.390
Usually, when the Lord brings up

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:50.470
something that many times, it's

00:01:50.480 --> 00:01:52.950
a major prayer topic.

00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:58.190
In fact, I don't think

00:01:58.190 --> 00:01:58.200
there's

00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.430
any time that he's ever

00:01:59.440 --> 00:02:01.190
brought up something 80 times; I

00:02:02.320 --> 00:02:05.310
was shocked myself.

