He said to us that there was

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:26.430
major corruption in Michigan,

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.630
Ohio,

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:34.710
Pennsylvania,

00:02:34.710 --> 00:02:34.720
and

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:36.190
California.

