I saw California,

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:40.030
Pennsylvania,

00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:42.710
and Boston,

00:02:42.710 --> 00:02:42.720
Massachusetts—a

00:02:42.720 --> 00:02:45.430
