00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:53.390
I was looking, just like

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:56.070
what we saw about Minnesota;

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:58.150
the Lord said there was a deeper level

00:02:58.160 --> 00:03:00.710
