00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:04.870
Las Vegas,

00:03:04.880 --> 00:03:08.030
Ohio, Boston, and Fetterman.

00:03:08.040 --> 00:03:10.030
And then

00:03:10.040 --> 00:03:12.190
as we were praying,

00:03:12.200 --> 00:03:13.750
this jacket's

00:03:13.760 --> 00:03:15.470
getting on my nerves. He saw a baby

00:03:15.470 --> 00:03:15.480
snake.

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:18.150
I

00:03:18.150 --> 00:03:18.160
was

00:03:18.160 --> 00:03:20.030
trying to blend in with the

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:21.550
background. It kind of looks good with

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:23.110
what he's been working on.

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:26.230
That's

00:03:26.240 --> 00:03:27.670
prophetic;

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:29.750
the Lord showed that to me in a

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:30.910
vision

00:03:30.920 --> 00:03:33.830
and Braden created it.

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:35.870
All of the things that the Lord has been

00:03:35.880 --> 00:03:37.550
showing us

00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:41.070
through the last two years, he's

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:43.150
putting it on there and he made it out

00:03:43.160 --> 00:03:46.150
