00:03:46.160 --> 00:03:48.230
to it as we talk

00:03:48.240 --> 00:03:49.870
just for fun.

00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:57.590
The Lord's into having fun, too. I

00:03:57.600 --> 00:03:59.030
thought it was interesting because as I was

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:02.030
