00:04:23.920 --> 00:04:27.630
2028's coming with Elon Musk and JD

00:04:27.640 --> 00:04:29.030
Vance.

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:31.030
Jerome Powell is looking for a job in

00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:33.128
2026.

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:37.950
Weather manipulation in the back with

00:04:37.960 --> 00:04:40.470
the tornado.

00:04:40.480 --> 00:04:42.790
Putin using a weapon that we've never

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:45.230
seen before back

00:04:45.230 --> 00:04:45.240
there—it

00:04:45.240 --> 00:04:46.870
