00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:48.270
not.

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:51.990
Kim Jong-un has the

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.190
USSR rocket coming down the Mississippi

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:56.110
River.

00:04:56.120 --> 00:04:59.190
Black Swan event with

00:04:59.200 --> 00:05:02.710
Emmanuel Macron concerning the Olympics

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:05.110
and Paris;

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:07.843
he's on the black swan riding it.

00:05:09.760 --> 00:05:12.070
And then we have Pinocchio down

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:14.990
