00:08:15.080 --> 00:08:19.990
George W. Bush.

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.870
Kim saw this.

00:08:21.880 --> 00:08:23.910
And I think this is interesting because

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:26.310
right after

00:08:26.320 --> 00:08:28.510
I was shown the judges, I saw

00:08:28.520 --> 00:08:31.510
