00:08:56.920 --> 00:08:59.390
video, just like us. But

00:08:59.400 --> 00:09:02.150
here you go.

00:10:37.160 --> 00:10:40.190
So, like I

00:10:40.200 --> 00:10:42.310
said, I don't add to or take away from

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:44.230
anything,

00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:45.990
