00:13:42.280 --> 00:13:44.870
before the drama started,

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:46.630
back

00:13:46.640 --> 00:13:49.470
in November.

00:13:49.480 --> 00:13:52.070
The Lord showed us that, and

00:13:52.080 --> 00:13:55.950
